perceive those &lt;BR&gt;objects, mind thinks of a notional being that is fa=\r\nr more complicated &lt;BR&gt;than the objective reality represented by it! It is =\r\ninfluenced by many &lt;BR&gt;notions arising in our conditioning and not just bas=\r\ned on the concrete &lt;BR&gt;objective reality. Again, such notions can be identi=\r\nfied and rejected as &lt;BR&gt;illusions.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;As you identify and reject each =\r\nlayer of obvious illusion about your &lt;BR&gt;sense of who you are, who/what you=\r\n are dealing with, you eventually &lt;BR&gt;realize unconditioned Self. Until the=\r\nn, &quot;jaganmithya&quot; is a meaningless &lt;BR&gt;and also perhaps a dangerous notion.&lt;=\r\nBR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Best regards,&lt;BR&gt;Narasimha&lt;BR&gt;--------------------------------------=\r\n--------------------&lt;BR&gt;Free Jyotish Software,\n Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyoti=\r\nsh Writings,&lt;BR&gt;&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri T=\r\narpana:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;A href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot; rel=3Dnofollow targe=\r\nt=3D_blank&gt;http://www.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Films that make a differen=\r\nce: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://saraswatifilms.org/&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank&gt;h=\r\nttp://SaraswatiFilms.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Spirituality: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://groups.yaho=\r\no.com/group/vedic-wisdom&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank&gt;http://groups.yaho=\r\no.com/group/vedic-wisdom&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Jyotish writings: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://groups.=\r\nyahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings&quot; rel=3Dnofollow target=3D_blank&gt;http://grou=\r\nps.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Twitter ID: @homam108&lt;BR&gt;--------=\r\n--------------------------------------------------&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Dear Narasim=\r\nha,&lt;BR&gt;&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt;&gt; Jagat isnt mithya. Brahman is satya &amp; jagat 2 i=\r\ns satya.&lt;BR&gt;&gt;&gt; Neither mirror nor ur image in it